    "title": "U.S. stocks close higher | The Star",
    "text": "NEW YORK, Nov. 22 (Xinhua) -- U.S. stocks ended higher on Friday.\nThe Dow Jones Industrial Average rose 426.16 points, or 0.97 percent, to 44,296.51. The S&P 500 added 20.63 points, or 0.35 percent, to 5,969.34. The Nasdaq Composite Index increased 31.23 points, or 0.16 percent, to 19,003.65.",
